{"type":"message","id":"48b65ce8","parentId":"53cf68da","timestamp":"2026-03-23T16:04:00.262Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_phb3y1778x0i_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"diff --git a/memory/active-projects.md b/memory/active-projects.md\r\nindex 91c35e2..456ba7f 100644\r\n--- a/memory/active-projects.md\r\n+++ b/memory/active-projects.md\r\n@@ -6,10 +6,20 @@ _Last updated: 2026-03-21_\r\n \r\n ## ≡ƒÜÇ Current Focus\r\n \r\n+### CodeCause ΓÇö Causal Coding Agent (NEW 2026-03-22)\r\n+**Goal:** Build a system that codes better than any current LLM via causal reasoning, not pattern matching\r\n+**Architecture:** Causal World Model + Dual-Head (infant) + Temporal Attention + Agent Planner\r\n+**Why:** Bottleneck is planning/debugging, not generation. Current LLMs guess next token; CodeCause *knows* what code does.\r\n+**Product path:** component-crate premium ΓÇö causal graph indexer + fine-tuned decoder\r\n+**Status:** Architecture designed, awaiting first prototype (causal graph indexer)\r\n+**Location:** `C:/dev/code-cause/` (to be scaffolded)\r\n+\r\n+### Build Our Own Gateway ΓÇö hold2\r\n+\r\n ### Build Our Own Gateway ΓÇö hold2\r\n **Goal:** Replace OpenClaw's agent loop with lean custom context layer\r\n **Why:** Bootstrap files injected every turn burn tokens. TOOLS.md is 54KB. We want full control.\r\n-**Stack:** Paperspace Gradient (A5000 30GB) ΓåÆ vLLM + fastapi ΓåÆ OpenClaw routes to our endpoint\r\n+**Stack:** Paperspace Gradient (cloud GPU) ΓåÆ vLLM + fastapi ΓåÆ OpenClaw routes to our endpoint\r\n **Model:** `HauhauCS/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B-Uncensored-HauhauCS-Aggressive` (Q4_K_M ~20GB VRAM)\r\n - Qwen3.5-35B MoE (~3B active/token, 35B total)\r\n - 0/465 refusals ΓÇö fully uncensored"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1306,"aggregated":"diff --git a/memory/active-projects.md b/memory/active-projects.md\r\nindex 91c35e2..456ba7f 100644\r\n--- a/memory/active-projects.md\r\n+++ b/memory/active-projects.md\r\n@@ -6,10 +6,20 @@ _Last updated: 2026-03-21_\r\n \r\n ## ≡ƒÜÇ Current Focus\r\n \r\n+### CodeCause ΓÇö Causal Coding Agent (NEW 2026-03-22)\r\n+**Goal:** Build a system that codes better than any current LLM via causal reasoning, not pattern matching\r\n+**Architecture:** Causal World Model + Dual-Head (infant) + Temporal Attention + Agent Planner\r\n+**Why:** Bottleneck is planning/debugging, not generation. Current LLMs guess next token; CodeCause *knows* what code does.\r\n+**Product path:** component-crate premium ΓÇö causal graph indexer + fine-tuned decoder\r\n+**Status:** Architecture designed, awaiting first prototype (causal graph indexer)\r\n+**Location:** `C:/dev/code-cause/` (to be scaffolded)\r\n+\r\n+### Build Our Own Gateway ΓÇö hold2\r\n+\r\n ### Build Our Own Gateway ΓÇö hold2\r\n **Goal:** Replace OpenClaw's agent loop with lean custom context layer\r\n **Why:** Bootstrap files injected every turn burn tokens. TOOLS.md is 54KB. We want full control.\r\n-**Stack:** Paperspace Gradient (A5000 30GB) ΓåÆ vLLM + fastapi ΓåÆ OpenClaw routes to our endpoint\r\n+**Stack:** Paperspace Gradient (cloud GPU) ΓåÆ vLLM + fastapi ΓåÆ OpenClaw routes to our endpoint\r\n **Model:** `HauhauCS/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B-Uncensored-HauhauCS-Aggressive` (Q4_K_M ~20GB VRAM)\r\n - Qwen3.5-35B MoE (~3B active/token, 35B total)\r\n - 0/465 refusals ΓÇö fully uncensored","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774281840262}}
